title: Goimpy (Comte François Louis Edmond Gabriel Martz de)
original_title: Goimpy (Comte François Louis Edmond Gabriel Martz de)
body: At the Naval Academy in Paris, there is a manuscript titled 'Observations faites à Aveiro et à Funchal', authored by Count François L. E. G. M. de Goimpy. We are unaware of when these observations were made, as well as their nature.
